1
00:01:29,470 --> 00:01:32,940
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:36,200
[Episode 18]

3
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:40,160
Yanzhi.

4
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:45,500
Nan Yanzhi.

5
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:49,000
Open your eyes.

6
00:03:28,270 --> 00:03:29,390
Mother.

7
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:31,710
I finally got the antidote.

8
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:33,240
Wait for me.

9
00:04:27,010 --> 00:04:27,970
Yanzhi,

10
00:04:28,170 --> 00:04:30,300
don't blame me for being too ruthless.

11
00:04:30,330 --> 00:04:31,630
If it weren't for this,

12
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:33,840
how could we have fooled Meng Shuo

13
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:35,480
and the entire Lingya Tower?

14
00:05:04,310 --> 00:05:05,940
[Virtue and Merit in Equal Splendor]

15
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:09,220
Mother.

16
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,840
Mother.

17
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,720
Mother!

18
00:05:32,340 --> 00:05:33,540
Mother?

19
00:05:34,090 --> 00:05:35,159
Mother.

20
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,600
Mr. Wu,

21
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,180
where is my mother?

22
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:10,400
[Tomb of the Late Father, Nan Shiren]

23
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:12,410
[Tomb of the Late Mother, Madam Yang]

24
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,320
Please.

25
00:06:31,330 --> 00:06:32,840
[Auspice from the East]

26
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,930
Uncle, I'm sorry

27
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,880
for keeping you waiting.

28
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:35,930
Not at all.

29
00:06:36,159 --> 00:06:37,890
You came at just the right time.

30
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,409
Please, have a seat.

31
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:41,920
Go ask

32
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,659
why Jingjing hasn't come yet.

33
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,600
Yes.

34
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,720
My Lady,

35
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,840
Mr. Liu has been waiting for a long time.

36
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:49,500
You should at least go see him.

37
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,440
Otherwise, snubbing him like this

38
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:53,700
might bring shame to the Prime Minister.

39
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,560
Given my current looks, I don't believe

40
00:07:00,290 --> 00:07:02,620
anyone would truly be willing to marry me.

41
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,850
We still haven't found
the killer of Nian'an,

42
00:07:05,850 --> 00:07:07,080
and you want me to remarry.

43
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:08,150
No way!

44
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:09,150
Jingjing,

45
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:11,000
I want Liu Yuan to marry into our family.

46
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:13,000
He is also an imperial scholar.

47
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:15,160
He is no worse than Shen Nian'an.

48
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:17,040
Nian'an is the only one I love.

49
00:07:18,030 --> 00:07:20,290
I'll never love anyone else in this life.

50
00:07:21,140 --> 00:07:22,100
Jingjing,

51
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:26,360
Liu Yuan and Shen Nian'an
were close friends.

52
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,100
He has

53
00:07:28,290 --> 00:07:29,290
a good reputation

54
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:31,460
-for both his talent and character.
-I've made up my mind!

55
00:07:31,460 --> 00:07:32,920
Don't push me any further!

56
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,800
Matters of marriage

57
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,280
are decided by parents

58
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,540
and matchmakers' words!

59
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:39,600
You are not allowed to act on your own!

60
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,760
Is that so?

61
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,640
If you insist, Father,

62
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,580
I'll have no choice but to do this!

63
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,840
Jingjing,

64
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:49,590
I just want you to find a good husband.

65
00:07:49,610 --> 00:07:51,960
Why are you trying to kill yourself?

66
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,200
Father,

67
00:08:02,570 --> 00:08:04,170
my face has been disfigured.

68
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,940
Surely no one will be willing to marry me.

69
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,200
As for my marriage,

70
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:14,220
you don't need to worry about it anymore.

71
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:15,750
My Lady,

72
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,660
why did you have to do that?

73
00:08:17,660 --> 00:08:19,300
Even if you don't want to remarry,

74
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:21,700
you didn't have to
ruin yourself like that.

75
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,160
My Lady!

76
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,760
Your husband is already gone,

77
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:26,600
but life still has to go on.

78
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,600
Isn't that right?

79
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:30,200
If it weren't to avenge Nian'an,

80
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,840
I'm afraid
I would have died with him long ago!

81
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,299
But the Prime Minister...

82
00:08:34,470 --> 00:08:35,640
Help me tell them

83
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:38,530
that it's inconvenient for me
to receive guests.

84
00:09:01,090 --> 00:09:03,300
Why didn't you just kill me back then?

85
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:04,640
Why?

86
00:09:07,090 --> 00:09:09,450
Why?

87
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:30,390
I don't have a mother anymore.

88
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:34,040
I'll never see my mother again.

89
00:09:45,510 --> 00:09:46,490
Auntie,

90
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:47,940
it's all my fault.

91
00:09:48,580 --> 00:09:49,710
If it weren't for me,

92
00:09:49,830 --> 00:09:51,890
they wouldn't have found this place.

93
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:53,410
I implicated you.

94
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,370
Wujiu.

95
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:57,200
It's not your fault.

96
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:02,080
If you truly want
to repay my family's kindness,

97
00:10:03,250 --> 00:10:04,410
please...

98
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:10,910
take good care of Yanzhi.

99
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:15,780
Mother!

100
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:31,270
Does it still hurt?

101
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:35,170
Compared to the torture you've suffered,

102
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:39,640
my injuries are nothing.

103
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:41,720
Master.

104
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,320
From now on,

105
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:47,750
you don't need to worry about me anymore.

106
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:49,810
Don't shoulder it all by yourself anymore.

107
00:10:49,810 --> 00:10:51,860
I want to fight alongside you.

108
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,240
For my parents

109
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,120
and for you.

110
00:10:54,660 --> 00:10:56,520
Let's go make them pay what they owe

111
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,280
together.

112
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:04,240
Okay.

113
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:06,540
We'll do it together.

114
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,360
Master.

115
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:58,160
So you knew Shen Nian'an.

116
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,360
All those years,

117
00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:03,460
he had been investigating the mastermind
behind the Lingya Tower,

118
00:12:03,460 --> 00:12:04,580
Hei Ya.

119
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:06,650
[Hei Ya will show up soon. Come quickly]

120
00:12:06,170 --> 00:12:08,230
Unfortunately, I was still too late.

121
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,690
Before I could meet him,

122
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,200
he was murdered.

123
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:13,490
No wonder the killer was so brutal.

124
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,280
So it was Hei Ya.

125
00:12:16,580 --> 00:12:18,090
So if we follow this lead,

126
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,520
we can find Hei Ya, right?

127
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:20,320
Yes.

128
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:22,890
Later, through some investigations,

129
00:12:22,890 --> 00:12:23,950
I found some clues

130
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:25,960
in Prime Minister Lin's Mansion.

131
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:27,690
The Prime Minister's Mansion?

132
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:30,180
Yanzhi,

133
00:12:30,590 --> 00:12:32,070
I need your help now.

